    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Acorn 工作流&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /blog/decoding-workload-specification/2_hu20bf1948d058bcfdf163328f79f19b1a_179658_492ba195cbd05591b751479fefe20ef7.webp 400w,
               /blog/decoding-workload-specification/2_hu20bf1948d058bcfdf163328f79f19b1a_179658_ae2987c54c4c92a2475c8d6cde183350.webp 760w,
               /blog/decoding-workload-specification/2_hu20bf1948d058bcfdf163328f79f19b1a_179658_1200x1200_fit_q75_h2_lanczos_3.webp 1200w&#34;
               src=&#34;https://lib.jimmysong.io/blog/decoding-workload-specification/2_hu20bf1948d058bcfdf163328f79f19b1a_179658_492ba195cbd05591b751479fefe20ef7.webp&#34;
               width=&#34;760&#34;
               height=&#34;336&#34;
